      "date": "2014-01-28 04:31:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e3efc6ce-87d4-11e3-b26e-52540035b04c).  Ran 6 tests.  No failures.",
